title: The Christmas Tree
creator: Anonymous
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of The Christmas Tree by Anonymous. This was the Weekly Poetry project for December 19, 2010. This poem taken from Christmas Entertainments by Alice Maude Kellogg (ed), containing fancy drills, acrostics, motion songs, tableaux, short plays, recitations in costume for children of five to fifteen years. (from book introduction) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, and for further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. M4B format available
subject: librivox; literature; audiobook; poetry; children; nature
